{"tid":386203,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"鐘意左一個本身有男朋友嘅女仔","createTime":"2017-09-03T16:51:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-04T09:12:32.000Z","uid":141997,"like":1,"dislike":64,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bbbcef743edb98b6d5dcf859556a5b973eaf38bd","tid":386203,"uid":141997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T16:51:01.000Z","msg":"是咁的...個個女仔係番工先識嘅...<br />\n咁有一次我就膽粗粗主動Whatsapp 俾佢同佢傾計<br />\n傾計過程中得知佢有男朋友感情麻麻，因為佢男朋友大男人主意，有少少霸道，好易嬲！<br />\n再加上有次佢番工頭痛唔舒服，佢男朋友就過左黎我間公司俾藥佢食！ <br />\n<br />\n到左依家，我地日日都傾計，大家有say good morning/good night ，琴日仲買左啲零食比佢番工休息時間有得食！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都唔知依家點算好...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果依家表白，佢一定會拒絕！<br />\n有人會話挽曖昧關係一定係高手，仲好過拍拖！<br />\n <br />\n好亂吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9dda078c82de57fd3ccad0af6fc578dc53b31a2","tid":386203,"uid":6111,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T17:02:28.000Z","msg":"首先 挽你老母<br />\n第二 如果佢男朋友真係咁差既佢自然會分手<br />\n洗咩你差隻腳埋去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf980585041d796faf8b1384ad02102eaac98509","tid":386203,"uid":128415,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T17:02:56.000Z","msg":"明明做狗公，又要扮君子 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e69cbd1abc473e7de69b3a6ff1df33c148821cd","tid":386203,"uid":56688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T17:12:21.000Z","msg":"人地仲一齊緊"},{"pid":"fcc7955363042e1390d01ad1a28e9aacc5de051a","tid":386203,"uid":127283,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T17:15:21.000Z","msg":"挽你老母死狗公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d710ca30cb9caa70b31a6fed192e5964ed593e0d","tid":386203,"uid":76527,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T17:17:56.000Z","msg"